article_title: Trader Joe's, Home Depot and the Unresolved Fairness Issue Inside ObamaCare

article_metadata.description: As the country waits for the ObamaCare exchanges to go live, every few days there is a new headline like this one: "Trader Joe’s Explains Why It’s Cutting Health Benefits For Part Timers." Or this one: "Home Depot Sending 20,000 Part-Timers to Health Exchanges."
